Text: Since I never used simulink I'm not 100% if there's something missing so pls report any bugs!

Don't bother downloading this for think this is full Matlab. This contains only the environment with only 1 toolbox installed. There is no symbolic math toolbox and all others.
It is useless. Better save yourself the time to download 1GB for nothing.
ignore medwatt's comment. the majority of matlab users dont use its toolboxes, especcially students.

Yes, I agree, but the symbolic toolbox is very very important. Most students want to do integration to see an expression but not to get a numerical answer. 
I say it once again. This version doesn't have THE SYMBOLIC TOOLBOX so you cannot perform symbolic maths.

Second on ignoring medwatt's comment. MATLAB, even if you buy it, does NOT come with a symbolic toolbox and CANNOT natively perform symbolic calculations. You have to get the symbolic toolbox separately.
